article.description: — Mason Archambault scored 25 points to lead six in double figures and South Dakota defeated Omaha 105-70 on Saturday,
article.headline: Archambault scores 25 in South Dakota's rout of Omaha
article.linkText: Archambault scores 25 in South Dakota's rout of Omaha
article.story: VERMILLION, S.D. -- — Mason Archambault scored 25 points to lead six in double figures and South Dakota defeated Omaha 105-70 on Saturday, Hunter Goodrick had 10 points and a game-high 13 rebounds for the Coyotes (10-7, 3-3 Summit). Frankie Fidler and Felix Lemetti had 11 points each for the Mavericks (3-16, 2-6). —-
